metadata.name: FVCK_AVATAR// #1
metadata.description:
You are billions of gigaparsecs away from earth, floating on a rust-coloured planet. The sky is black and the ground is rumbling. The dream feels vivid and real.

Sculptures made of liquid metal and glowing crystal embellish the planets in LVCIDIA. Created long ago by intergalactic artists, they express the fragility of our existence and the beauty of our humanity.

Today, they are yours to explore.
